node.text:
Hold on to your butts, Gamers! @Qualcomm recently announced the Smartphone for Snapdragon Insiders, designed by Asus, featuring Snapdragon Elite Gaming which means all the speed you need for elite gamers everywhere. One of the Snapdragon 888 5G Mobile Platform highlights is the Qualcomm Adreno 660 GPU for 35% faster graphics rendering, true 10-bit color HDR, and the first mobile platform with Variable Rate Shading for 30% greater resolutions, higher frame rates, and low power requirements.
 
Be a part of the @SnapdragonInsiders community to get behind-the-scenes access and enter for a chance to win a special edition smartphone made JUST for Snapdragon Insiders! Join at SnapdragonInsiders.com #QualcommPartner

node.title: Snapdragon Elite Gaming on the Smartphone for Snapdragon Insiders
